  "title": "Copper Ore",
  "summaries": [
    "<b>Copper Ore</b> is an early game <linked>ore</linked>, which spawns on the <linked>surface</linked> as well as in the <linked>Underground</linked> and <linked>Cavern</linked> layers. It is the weakest and most easily obtained tier of ore in the game. Its primary use is to make <linked>Copper Bars</linked>, which can be used to create the Copper tier of equipment. The equivalent of Copper Ore is <linked>Tin Ore</linked>, which will sometimes replace Copper in a world. <span class=\"eico i1 i2 i4 i5 i6\" title=\"Desktop, Console, Mobile, 3DS and Legacy tModLoader versions\"><b></b><i></i></span> Copper Ore has a small chance to appear as a <linked>bonus drop</linked> from <linked>slimes</linked>."
